<span class="head">2001 Best of CES Award Winners</span><br><br>
From over 200 innovative new products introduced, TechTV and CES honor the products
that are truly the &#147;Best of CES&#148;
<BR><BR>
The TechTV-appointed panel of product evaluators selected winners in each category according to their
innovative appeal, usability, usefulness, and affordability. In addition to the ten categories, two Best
of Show honors were given for &#147;Best Workstyle&#148; and &#147;Best Lifestyle&#148; products.
The winners, selected from the below group of finalists, are as follows:
<BR><BR>
<center>
<span class="head">BEST WORKSTYLE</span><br><BR>
<font size="2"><strong>Hughes Network Systems - Satellite Return DirecPC</font></strong>
<BR><BR>
<span class="head">BEST LIFESTYLE</span><br><BR>
<font size="2"><strong>DataPlay Inc. - DataPlay Digital Media</font></strong>
</center>
<BR><BR>

<span class="subhead">Home Automation and Networking</span>
<BR>
<b>Winner:</b>
<br>
Home Automated Living - HAL Deluxe
<br><br>
<b>Finalists:</b>
<ul>
	<li>Ucentric Systems - Home Networking Platform: Home area network connects all electronics</li>
	<li>Qubit - Home Gateway Interface: Webpad access Internet and ADT security</li>
</ul>
<BR>
<span class="subhead">Mobile Devices: PDAs and Other Personal Mobile Technology</span>
<BR>
<b>Winner:</b>
<br>
DataPlay - DataPlay Digital Media: a quarter-sized digital media costs $5 for 500 megabytes
<BR><BR>
<b>Finalists:</b>
<ul>
	<li>Xircom - Rex 6000 MicroPDA: a credit-card sized PDA</li>
	<li>Motorola - Accompli A009: PDA and phone together with color screen</li>
</ul>
<BR>
<span class="subhead">Audio: Mainstream Audio Devices</span>
<br>
<b>Winner:</b>
<br>
American Acoustic Development - AAD E-Series Lifestyle System: a great sounding speaker system
<BR><BR>
<b>Finalists:</b>
<ul>
	<li>Midwives - The Madplayer DB-4: interactive digital music player</li>
	<li>TDK Electronics Corp. - TDK Termor S-150: great sounding very inexpensive speakers</li>
</ul>
<BR>
<span class="subhead">Video: Television, Video Recorders, Personal Television</span>
<BR>
<b>Winner:</b>
<br>
Nokia</b> - Media Terminal: an Internet enabled set-top box
<BR><BR>
<b>Finalists:</b>
<ul>
	<li>Snapstream - Snapstream Media Personal Video Station: Turns your PC into a personal video server</li>
	<li>AccessDTV - DTV-1003: Turns your PC into a HDTV receiver</li>
</ul>
<BR>
<span class="subhead">Internet: Dedicated Internet and Email Devices</span>
<BR>
<b>Winner:</b>
<br>
Hughes Network Systems - Satellite Return DirecPC: Two way satellite-based Internet access
<BR><BR>
<b>Finalists:</b>
<ul>
	<li>Sony - E-Villa: an Internet appliance</li>
	<li>Qubit - Orbit: a Wireless webpad</li>
</ul>
<BR>
<span class="subhead">Digital Imaging: Digital Cameras, Scanners, Photo Paper, Etc</span>
<BR>
<b>Winner:</b>
<br>
SmaL Camera Technologies - Ultra Pocket Digital Camera: credit-card-sized 640X480 digital camera
<BR><BR>
<b>Finalists:</b>
<ul>
	<li>Digitech Products - LLC Digiviewer: digital binoculars with LCD display</li>
	<li>Ceiva - Internet Connected Digital Picture Frame LF2001: a digital picture frame</li>
</ul>
<BR>
<span class="subhead">Telephony: Cell Phones, Home Phones, Internet Phones, Etc.</span>
<BR>
<b>Winner:</b>
<br>
Seiko - Wearable Mobile Phone - a cell phone you wear on your wrist
<BR><BR>
<b>Finalists:</b>
<ul>
	<li>Nokia - 3390 Wireless Phone: a well made inexpensive cell phone</li>
	<li>Motorola -V Series V60 Phone: a very sleek clamshell cell phone</li>
</ul>
<BR>
<span class="subhead">Auto, Marine, and RV: If it&#146;s For Your Car, Truck, or Boat</span>
<BR>
<b>Winner:</b>
<br>
XM</b> - Satellite Radio System
<BR><BR>
<b>Finalists:</b>
<ul>
	<li>Donnelly Corp. - VideoMirror with BabyVue and ReversAid: an in vehicle camera system
to spy on baby and back of car</li>
	<li>Sirius Radio - Sirius Satellite Radio</li>
</ul>
<BR>
<span class="subhead">Specialty Audio: High End Audio Hardware</span>
<BR>
<b>Winner:</b>
<br>
Sonigistix - Monsoon FPF Series Speakers: great sounding flat panel speakers
<BR><BR>
<b>Finalists:</b>
<ul>
	<li>Linn Products - Limited Linn Knekt Kivor music system: hard disk based CD player
	<li>S.A.P. - Relaxa 1: Magnetic levitation-based vibration isolation system
</ul>
<BR>
<span class="subhead">Accessories and Personal Electronics: Everything Else</span>
<br>
<b>Winner:</b>
<br>
Path Group/IXOS - CaP 280-easy to install coax cable
<BR><BR>
<b>Finalists:</b>
<ul>
	<li>Acer NeWeb Corp. - Phaser AA001: turns IR remote into RF remote
	<li>Gemini Industries - PROmote PRO100: universal remote you program with your PC
</ul>
<br>
&#147;The
competition was truly fierce&#148;, said Jim Louderback, TechTV&#146;s on-air host,
editorial director, and coordinator of the contest. &#147;I was very impressed with the overwhelming number of truly
impressive and innovative products. 2001 is going to be a great year for anyone that
loves consumer electronics. There are
some great new products coming soon. The judges decisions were difficult, but in the end, they came through,
selecting the most outstanding consumer technology products.&#148;
